<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Re: clerics and pvpers???</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?klog">klog</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 1:03 a.m. 13/2/2000<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Re: clerics and pvpers???<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=2320" TARGET=_self>Re: clerics and pvpers???</A> (Joruus Darevitam)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>I am a lvl 16 necro on vallon zek. First off you got a few things right. Clerics are very group pvp friendly cause they can heal their tanks to full which is a huge asset. BUT , in one on one fights clerics REALLY suck. Who ever it was you dueled the necro, mustnt have been very good. Blindess doesnt stop me from casting on you. blindess is good but i can still cast and my pet is still up ur butt. My pet makes it hard for u to heal, if you can still it wont matter. I once was being attacked by a halfling cleric that coned red. at first i thought just run, but instead i thought i would take a shot my pet was already on him. I casted my dots and NONE were resisted which was pritty lucky. He would blind me and try to root, root dont matter shadow step cast , cancle magic ect. I got him runing before he could get a single bubble from me. Their DD isnt that good i can easily heal it off with one cast onf lifedrain spell. slowing them down makes it hard for them to run haha. I love clerics and i have made one before but in pvp they just arent that great besides enhacing a group for killing.

</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
